Class Enquiry

Object
Enquiry
public class Enquiry extends Object
Represents an enquiry submitted by an applicant regarding a specific BTO project. Enquiries include a message, sender information, and optional replies from officers or managers. Each enquiry is assigned a unique ID for reference. Used by both applicants and staff during the enquiry management process.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Javier
